{"tid":1200601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十一號唔好出嚟","createTime":"2019-06-10T19:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T20:48:48.000Z","uid":40855,"like":36,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"015af5454efed518acd97982e0511a660d1a9470","tid":1200601,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:13:17.000Z","msg":"有人話十二號朝早先集結，差佬有晒準備，所以要十一號晚去定先。<br />\n同理，差佬知你十一號晚去，咪一樣會準備定先。<br />\n<br />\n何不等十二號養足精力，一鼓作氣？<br />\n<br />\n如果十一號晚集結，係咪嗰晚夠人衝入去先？就算衝到，守唔守得住一晚？<br />\n點解唔等十二號日頭，幾萬人圍住做後援先一鼓作氣爆入去，幾千人長期留守？"},{"pid":"eee91839e6beca7b44bc9a4f09d61936d7a7ac1f","tid":1200601,"uid":40855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86eb9b02814bfaa4f47e8ed33225fffb31613588","tid":1200601,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:21:47.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"3e41e6f16e168f9009a977bd26e552cca5d7d015","tid":1200601,"uid":136415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9626907bf6a2eccb35874e55b04a39d155140095","tid":1200601,"uid":179962,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:23:13.000Z","msg":"其實唔好留守<br />\n每個星期六晚出黎聚<br />\n好似法國咁"},{"pid":"93c9631f652ffc44bb1589d90a438d4de5222f8d","tid":1200601,"uid":37713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:23:30.000Z","msg":"主要係入夜肯定會少啲人<br />\n而少啲人加上入夜 啲狗會比起日頭更加埋沒人性<br />\n<br />\n總之萬事小心啦<br />\n唔夠人就唔好硬頂 be water my friend"},{"pid":"6c891543669ab71a39e050df88556b88fbf31fd1","tid":1200601,"uid":179962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:23:40.000Z","msg":"要既係持續 唔係一晚半晚"},{"pid":"f5f2a3ac77055dc56d5b8ba28600efad56661a75","tid":1200601,"uid":179962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93c9631f652ffc44bb1589d90a438d4de5222f8d","tid":1200601,"uid":37713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"ci